# Interactive Learning Platform – Implementation Plan

Build a full-stack interactive programming education platform called **CodePath** — students learn Python (and more languages), solve DSA problems, earn XP, level up, and track their daily streak.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This builds a complete working app with realistic seeded data. We start focused: **Python** as the first language + **Arrays & Strings** as the first DSA module, with a scalable foundation to add more later.

