### Backend — `f:/futf/backend`

#### [NEW] Project scaffold
- `package.json` with Express, Mongoose, JWT, bcrypt, cors, dotenv, nodemon
- `src/index.js` — app entry point
- `.env` — MongoDB URI, JWT secret, Judge0 API key

#### [NEW] Models
- `src/models/User.js` — `{ name, email, password, xp, level, streak, lastActive, completedLessons[], badges[] }`
- `src/models/Course.js` — `{ language, title, modules[{ title, lessons[{ title, content, codeExample, challenge }] }] }`
- `src/models/Problem.js` — `{ title, description, difficulty, tags[], testCases[], starterCode }`
- `src/models/Submission.js` — `{ userId, problemId, code, status, language, runtime }`

#### [NEW] Routes
- `src/routes/auth.js` — POST `/register`, POST `/login`
- `src/routes/user.js` — GET `/me`, PUT `/progress` (update XP, streak, completedLessons)
- `src/routes/courses.js` — GET `/courses`, GET `/courses/:id`, GET `/courses/:id/lessons/:lessonId`
- `src/routes/problems.js` — GET `/problems`, GET `/problems/:id`, POST `/problems/:id/submit`
- `src/routes/execute.js` — POST `/execute` (proxy to Judge0)

#### [NEW] Seed Data
- `src/seed/pythonCourse.js` — Full Python syllabus (Beginner → Advanced) with 3 modules, ~12 lessons
- `src/seed/dsaProblems.js` — 10 Arrays/Strings problems (Easy/Medium/Hard) with test cases

