### Frontend — `f:/futf/frontend`

#### [NEW] Next.js 14 App (App Router)

Tech stack: **Next.js 14 + Tailwind CSS + Framer Motion + Monaco Editor + ShadCN UI**

#### Key Pages & Components

| Route | Description |
|---|---|
| `/` | Landing page — hero, features, CTA |
| `/login` `/register` | Auth pages |
| `/dashboard` | User dashboard — XP, streak, progress |
| `/learn` | Language selection grid |
| `/learn/[language]` | Course overview with module tree |
| `/learn/[language]/[lessonId]` | Lesson page — concept + Monaco Editor + quiz |
| `/dsa` | DSA problem listing with filters |
| `/dsa/[problemId]` | Problem solving page (split: description + Monaco editor) |
| `/profile` | Profile, badges, achievements |

#### [NEW] Core Components
- `Navbar` — responsive navigation, user XP indicator
- `XPBar` — animated progress bar showing level progress
- `StreakBadge` — fire icon with current streak count
- `LessonCard` — lesson tile showing completion status
- `CodeEditor` — Monaco editor wrapper with language support
- `QuizModal` — animated quiz overlay per lesson
- `ProblemCard` — DSA problem tile (difficulty chip, tags)
- `AnimatedDiagram` — Framer Motion visualizations (array ops, stack)
- `AuthProvider` — JWT token context for all protected routes

#### [NEW] Design System
- Dark theme by default (VSCode-inspired dark background)
- Accent: vibrant purple-to-blue gradient (`#7C3AED → #2563EB`)
- Typography: **Inter** from Google Fonts
- Glassmorphism cards, subtle glow on hover
- Smooth page transitions with Framer Motion

